{
  "_doc": [
    "Least-privilege IAM policy for the deploy IAM user/role.",
    "Attach this policy (and ONLY this policy) to the IAM identity",
    "whose access keys end up in ~/.aws/credentials. The policy lets",
    "the deploy script publish to the explorer prefix and nothing",
    "else; it cannot delete the bucket, modify CORS, touch the",
    "ingestion widget's prefix, or read other AWS services.",
    "",
    "Apply via the AWS console (IAM > Policies > Create policy > JSON",
    "tab > paste this) or via CLI:",
    "  aws iam create-policy \\",
    "    --policy-name KWExplorerS3Deploy \\",
    "    --policy-document file://apps/explorer/aws/iam-policy.json",
    "",
    "Then attach to your deploy user:",
    "  aws iam attach-user-policy \\",
    "    --user-name <username> \\",
    "    --policy-arn arn:aws:iam::467685081786:policy/KWExplorerS3Deploy"
  ],
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "ListBucketScopedToExplorerPrefix",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": ["s3:ListBucket"],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::3dx-kwforge-widgets",
      "Condition": {
        "StringLike": {
          "s3:prefix": ["3dx-knowledge-explorer/*", "3dx-knowledge-explorer"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "ReadWriteExplorerObjectsOnly",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:PutObject",
        "s3:GetObject",
        "s3:DeleteObject",
        "s3:AbortMultipartUpload"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::3dx-kwforge-widgets/3dx-knowledge-explorer/*"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "ConfirmIdentity",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": ["sts:GetCallerIdentity"],
      "Resource": "*"
    }
  ]
}
